14:40.title: A Journey to Modernize Our Software Systems
14:40.description: Have you ever given a thought on how to modernize 15 years old software systems? How about if they are written in 2 different countries by engineers from different tech backgrounds and in fact formerly being competitors? Do you think it is quick and easy to move from a data center to a modern cloud infrastructure? I’d talk about challenges and complexity to transform mature systems with millions of users to be supported around the clock. Join the session to find out about various ways to go about this journey, what worked and what didn't work for us.
